Gisiel  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Dźwierzuty, Szczytno County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  north-east of Dźwierzuty,  north of Szczytno, and  east of the regional capital Olsztyn.
The village has a population of 94.
